==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cranioscopist
<hw>Cra`ni*os"co*pist</hw> <pr>(kr?`n?-?s"k?-p?st)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>One skilled in, or who practices, cranioscopy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It was found of equal dimension in a literary man whose skull
puzzied the <qex>cranioscopists</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cranioscopy</ent>⟦br⟧
